        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Tradeable Performance Standard Act</strong></p> <p>This bill establishes the Greenhouse Gas Pollution Reduction Program, which creates (1) enforceable targets to reduce greenhouse gas emissions from cogeneration facilities, electric facilities, and thermal facilities; (2) a system to allow such facilities to achieve the targets through a voluntary emission trading program; and (3) a thermal energy reporting program.</p> <p><br> </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
